Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.60,0:01:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.09,0:01:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使你不能读到这封信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.05,0:01:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.94,0:01:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也让我写下对你的思绪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.06,0:01:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你作为库鲁吉斯的少年士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.22,0:01:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被强迫去战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.19,0:01:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变得只能在战场上活下去的你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.84,0:02:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追求和平的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.23,0:02:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你 应该是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.50,0:02:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.74,0:02:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你选择的道路 无法交汇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.49,0:02:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你使用着武力 去消除世界上的纷争
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.71,0:02:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使那能实现
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.28,0:02:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的幸福 又会在哪儿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.83,0:02:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你背负着罪恶 被伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.09,0:02:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此也要继续战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.64,0:02:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的你的生活方式 不管怎么看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.70,0:02:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都觉得可悲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.83,0:02:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将自己的幸福 与他人共享
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.46,0:03:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为 将这份和睦散布开
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.53,0:03:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能与真正的和平相连
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.07,0:03:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 也请你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.58,0:03:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住自己的幸福吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.18,0:03:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.09,0:03:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我祈祷着幸福会到访你的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.86,0:03:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.37,0:03:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.09,0:03:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾美
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.28,0:03:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.86,0:04:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我离开了卡塔隆 作为Gundam Meister活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为洛克昂·斯特拉特斯 去面对这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.94,0:04:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算被世界厌恶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.69,0:04:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我接受那份惩罚之前 我将不断战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.10,0:04:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还要过会才去你们那边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.38,0:04:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前 请等着我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.36,0:04:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾纽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.58,0:04:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界又再次改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.32,0:04:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是为此我们犯下的罪恶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.06,0:04:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夺去他人的生命的罪恶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.80,0:04:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.42,0:04:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界充满矛盾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.35,0:04:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己也充满了矛盾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.48,0:04:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那些必须要改变
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.38,0:04:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要找到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.12,0:05:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到我们活下去的意义 找到答案
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.21,0:05:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样 未来就托付给人类了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.36,0:05:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将成为维塔的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.65,0:05:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,静静地守护着你们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.99,0:05:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到「即将到来的对话」来临之时
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.21,0:05:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了 各位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.40,0:05:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是天人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.87,0:05:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了根绝战争的组织
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.68,0:05:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我们被世界抛弃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.50,0:05:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也将与世界继续对峙下去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算要行使武力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.42,0:05:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要作为世界的抑止力活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.37,0:05:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为如此 我们必须要存在下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.98,0:06:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了未来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.79,0:06:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机动战士Gundam OO Anastasia
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.79,0:06:32.27,A6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Anastasia原义指觉醒/复活的女性，鉴于接下来的情节\n 以及日本曾将一部1956年名为「Anastasia」的电影翻译为「追忆」，\n此处可同样翻译为「追忆」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.47,0:06:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊 莱尔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.86,0:06:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你选择了天人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.11,0:06:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 选择了作为Gundam Meister的生存之路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.42,0:06:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然唯独你 我不想你跟我走上同样的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.78,0:07:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狄兰迪家的血 果然是无可争议地相似啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.30,0:07:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊 莱尔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.03,0:07:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你是不一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.37,0:07:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要走你自己的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.99,0:07:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被过去所束缚的我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.32,0:07:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了改变世界 而接受了Gundam Meister的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.26,0:07:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算要夺去他人的性命 也要改变世界
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.53,0:07:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.13,0:07:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是对因为恐怖袭击而失去了家人的过去 进行的复仇而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.36,0:07:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心 一点也没有面向未来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.75,0:07:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是为了改变世界而战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.02,0:07:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己却完全没有改变
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.74,0:07:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱尔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.45,0:07:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你是不一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.31,0:07:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找到了未来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.18,0:07:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了战斗的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.05,0:08:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了人与人互相理解的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.29,0:08:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是多亏了那孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.30,0:08:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾纽·里特纳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.85,0:08:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 莱尔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.83,0:08:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.68,0:08:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直很在意我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.69,0:08:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.95,0:08:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密的操作 我大部分都已经习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.66,0:08:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾纽…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.99,0:08:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你虽然很聪明也很博识 但也挺迟钝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.95,0:08:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迟钝吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.84,0:08:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是一点 是相当
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.28,0:08:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.51,0:08:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 这也要我来说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.72,0:08:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是不说的话我就不明白嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.43,0:08:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我很迟钝嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.43,0:09:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 莱尔 能说来听听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.18,0:09:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.59,0:09:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哥哥的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.31,0:09:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有留下他的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.10,0:09:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我从初中的时候就寄宿在学校宿舍了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.10,0:09:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要住在宿舍？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.11,0:09:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为不想和能干的哥哥相比啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.80,0:09:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起战斗 还是选择了逃避的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.56,0:09:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你和哥哥一样 成为了Gundam Meister啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.88,0:09:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动机是不一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.98,0:09:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来我也没问过啊 艾纽你的家人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.06,0:09:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…家人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.43,0:09:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.56,0:10:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.50,0:10:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想说的话不说也行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.43,0:10:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾纽你现在在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.92,0:10:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要这样就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.30,0:10:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.85,0:10:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运真是讽刺啊 莱尔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.43,0:10:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你爱的女人 居然是原始变革体
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.81,0:10:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.81,0:10:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还用问吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.62,0:10:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要再一次让你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.80,0:10:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为我的女人！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.18,0:10:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不允许你说不！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.72,0:10:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.80,0:11:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要的东西就要抢到手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.08,0:11:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.24,0:11:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是变革者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.34,0:11:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.35,0:11:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾纽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.24,0:11:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来吧 艾纽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.46,0:11:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱尔…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.63,0:11:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.99,0:11:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.02,0:11:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾纽？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.08,0:11:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾纽！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.40,0:11:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变革者将引导人类
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.70,0:11:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 是更加进化的 绝对存在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.15,0:12:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人类看作是平等的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.25,0:12:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是无法忍受啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.14,0:12:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让你看看 力量的差距吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.16,0:12:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.65,0:12:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊 艾纽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.35,0:12:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾纽！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.82,0:12:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱尔 我明白你有多怨恨刹那的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.20,0:12:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像我无法忘记失去家人的痛楚一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.76,0:12:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为你会和我一样 被黑暗所吞噬…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.57,0:13:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你…就是你…就是你把艾纽…！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.35,0:13:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.13,0:13:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.89,0:13:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她要回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.40,0:13:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是作为变革者 而是作为人类
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.49,0:13:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到我们身边…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.41,0:13:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为你…！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.42,0:13:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.76,0:13:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾纽…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.77,0:13:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 从那时开始 你就改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.66,0:13:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 给老子动起来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.79,0:14:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也没资格说哥哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.07,0:14:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这家伙 不能饶恕！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.19,0:14:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别跑啊 混帐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.30,0:14:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.96,0:14:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.75,0:14:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.14,0:14:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把爸爸 妈妈 还有艾美…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.80,0:14:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连哥哥也…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.17,0:14:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱尔 我们互相理解的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.94,0:14:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱尔…我觉得自己是变革者真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.47,0:15:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.74,0:15:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是的话 就不会遇上你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.62,0:15:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 我们是互相理解的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.56,0:15:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 当然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.43,0:15:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.06,0:15:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢材！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.80,0:15:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 我已经抛弃了莱尔·狄兰迪的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.25,0:16:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我已经成为了天人的Gundam Meister 洛克昂·斯特拉特斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.26,0:16:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 妈妈 艾美
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.21,0:16:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有哥哥的灵魂 全都由我来背负
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.92,0:16:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 连艾纽的份也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.75,0:16:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK 那就放手去做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.12,0:16:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己选择的道路 在那道路上用最快的速度奔驰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.53,0:16:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩命地跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.66,0:16:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱尔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.13,0:16:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 洛克昂·斯特拉特斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.42,0:16:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狙击吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.81,0:16:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向着世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.11,0:16:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向着世界狙击吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.84,0:16:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？菲露特的双亲都在天人里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.35,0:17:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们都是第二代的Gundam Meister
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.48,0:17:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.43,0:17:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我多亏了你双亲才能战斗的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.23,0:17:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今日是忌日
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.01,0:17:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们俩的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.73,0:17:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.09,0:17:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.12,0:17:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是都死去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.79,0:17:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私立武装组织 天人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在那出生 长大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.21,0:17:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与伊奥利亚·肖汉博格的理念共鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.73,0:17:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将纷争从世界上清除
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.88,0:17:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有着如此崇高目的的组织
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.32,0:17:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 与那理想相反
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.47,0:17:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们被世界所厌恶 变成了为人疏远的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.52,0:17:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.54,0:17:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得那样也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.51,0:18:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用力量是无法永远支配人们的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.86,0:18:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那只会让战争不断重复发生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.25,0:18:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孕育憎恶 让人们互相伤害而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.46,0:18:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要连洛克昂的份一起…活下去啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.13,0:18:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.35,0:18:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请…改变世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.36,0:18:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.08,0:18:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然现在以武力为标志 作为抑止力来面对世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.28,0:18:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为 我们的存在变得真正没有必要的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.74,0:18:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终将会到来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.76,0:18:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像那天 刹那将战场上的人们的心灵相连那样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.01,0:19:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿人们能理解互相的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.79,0:19:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.96,0:19:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得能来到托勒密 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.10,0:19:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我们唯有通过战斗来面对世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.98,0:19:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此 现在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.43,0:19:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了能让因为纷争而流下的鲜血减少一些
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.99,0:19:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让和平到来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.42,0:19:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.58,0:19:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赌上这性命 前行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.33,0:20:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在思考活下去的意义？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.73,0:20:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那种思春期到来而踏上寻找自我的旅途的家伙么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.50,0:20:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷鲁亚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.92,0:20:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都过二十岁了还这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.67,0:20:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和玛莉都是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.63,0:20:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗 我们可是超兵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.45,0:20:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了战斗 脑子和身体这里那里都被改造过的怪物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.23,0:20:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的我们要做的事情只有一件
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.60,0:20:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是只有战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.07,0:20:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是你的生存意义啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.90,0:20:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 玛莉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.08,0:20:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 没事 阿雷鲁亚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.75,0:20:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉 就算我们的旅程已经快两年了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.80,0:20:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没有找到答案
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.09,0:20:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 只有这个我是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.84,0:20:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.78,0:21:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有谁…有谁…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.27,0:21:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有谁…能听到我的声音…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.22,0:21:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和我很像
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.75,0:21:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能听到我的声音吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.97,0:21:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪 你在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.06,0:21:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就在你眼前吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.26,0:21:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.03,0:21:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 能说话就很开心了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.82,0:21:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我一直都是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.39,0:21:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能来到这里 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.22,0:21:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.06,0:21:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.69,0:21:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.29,0:21:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.45,0:21:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.53,0:21:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.71,0:21:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是谁 为什么在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.86,0:21:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连名字也想不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.71,0:21:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我给你取个名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.87,0:21:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢…你的名字是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.03,0:21:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷鲁亚就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.26,0:22:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷鲁亚？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.80,0:22:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是用来感谢神的话语哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.09,0:22:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.57,0:22:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要感谢什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.45,0:22:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还用说嘛 是「活下去」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.50,0:22:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为活着 我才能再次见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.70,0:22:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算 你已经变成了索玛·皮瑞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.37,0:22:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.22,0:22:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止了 测试体E-57
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.10,0:22:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.30,0:22:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许动！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.15,0:22:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.99,0:22:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不叫那个名字！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.52,0:22:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这是真正的你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.32,0:22:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉…玛莉·帕法西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.97,0:22:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉…帕法西？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.97,0:22:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉·帕法西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.43,0:23:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你再次相遇 让我找到了生存的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.99,0:23:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己###明白
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.76,0:23:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要拯救你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.62,0:23:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个感觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.23,0:23:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,测试体E-57！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.56,0:23:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.95,0:23:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是玛莉吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.29,0:23:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我啊 阿雷鲁亚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.28,0:23:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.96,0:23:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超兵！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.92,0:23:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.24,0:23:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.90,0:23:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会再放开你了 玛莉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.99,0:23:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.10,0:23:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.49,0:23:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊 玛莉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.40,0:23:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算没了MS…！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.48,0:24:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能对付你这个瑕疵品…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.09,0:24:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.88,0:24:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉？玛莉·帕法西！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.27,0:24:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.41,0:24:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.89,0:24:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.59,0:24:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.36,0:24:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.29,0:24:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.12,0:24:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷…鲁亚
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.62,0:24:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.25,0:24:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你记起我了…？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.22,0:24:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷…鲁亚
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.84,0:24:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.69,0:24:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉！玛莉·帕法西！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.94,0:24:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我杀了他们
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.27,0:24:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴 和同胞
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.92,0:25:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这双手 把大家的生命…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.96,0:25:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一次剥夺了…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.62,0:25:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.67,0:25:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也杀了你一次
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.85,0:25:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候的攻击 我把另一个的你…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.45,0:25:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把哈雷鲁亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.01,0:25:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你添上了这道伤痕…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.25,0:25:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是！那是索玛·皮瑞斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.33,0:25:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你一样 皮瑞斯就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.93,0:25:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.81,0:25:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.35,0:25:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.86,0:25:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把索玛·皮瑞斯当成玛莉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.05,0:25:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我脑中只是想着你 想着要救你
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.38,0:25:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…现在那个实现了…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.39,0:25:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我该做什么才好
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.53,0:25:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的我 能为你做什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.00,0:25:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你告诉我这些 就很开心了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.99,0:26:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.28,0:26:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 我和你相遇了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.89,0:26:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有五感 只能用脑量子波来呼喊的我
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.08,0:26:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有回应的 只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.51,0:26:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏你 我才能感谢活下来这事
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.42,0:26:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够用这双眼来凝视着那样的你
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.21,0:26:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能跟你说话 能抚摸你…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.78,0:26:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的时光能到来…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.29,0:26:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.72,0:26:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神啊 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.16,0:26:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aleluia
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.19,0:26:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我由于你的…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.33,0:26:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你们愚蠢的行动失去了很多同胞和部下
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.55,0:26:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这份憎恨…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.75,0:26:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不可能忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.65,0:26:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请住手 大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.18,0:26:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请开枪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.19,0:26:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷鲁亚？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.69,0:26:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为交换 请把玛莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.73,0:27:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 请发誓再也不会把索玛·皮瑞斯卷入战争
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.73,0:27:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么 阿雷鲁亚
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.66,0:27:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 玛莉
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.64,0:27:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你能幸福地活下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.47,0:27:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请开枪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.00,0:27:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悉从尊意
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.00,0:27:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.18,0:27:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.18,0:27:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大…大佐？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.62,0:27:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在刚才 索玛·皮瑞斯中尉光荣战死了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.13,0:27:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了向上层部报告 我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.97,0:27:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.16,0:27:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米卢诺夫大佐！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.75,0:27:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只征用索玛·皮瑞斯进行对Gundam战
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.64,0:27:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而没有让她参加其他战斗的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.11,0:27:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很感谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.62,0:28:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种措辞 果然不是我所认识的中尉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.53,0:28:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 我身体中的索玛·皮瑞斯是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.72,0:28:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要成为…您的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.70,0:28:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.49,0:28:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这句话就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.64,0:28:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.50,0:28:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要活着…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.18,0:28:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.85,0:28:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他一起 幸福地活下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.66,0:28:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以来都非常感谢你 大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.13,0:28:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞鲁哥·斯米卢诺夫大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.53,0:28:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把玛莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.04,0:28:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 把索玛·皮瑞斯当成自己女儿一样对待
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.74,0:29:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直保护着她的斯米卢诺夫大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.04,0:29:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在和A-LAWS的战斗中…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.76,0:29:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大…大佐？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.07,0:29:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米卢诺夫大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.53,0:29:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐！！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.23,0:29:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争会夺去生命 生出新的仇恨
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.98,0:29:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我存在于那衍生出罪恶的连锁中
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.58,0:29:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉 就算我们的旅程已经快两年了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.65,0:29:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也还没有找到答案
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.88,0:29:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 只有这个我是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.76,0:29:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为活着
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.10,0:29:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为一直活着
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.54,0:29:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能再次见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.61,0:30:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是个毫无疑问的事实
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.59,0:30:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.28,0:30:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.79,0:30:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾经扣下扳机的我
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.20,0:30:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夺去了许多生命的我
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.12,0:30:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经无法再回到日常的生活中了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.82,0:30:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为如此 我更加不能逃避心中的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.62,0:30:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须得正视这些才行
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.89,0:30:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算包含了巨大的矛盾
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.51,0:30:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之中 我也想要去接受
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.95,0:30:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个旅途也是接受的其中一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.77,0:30:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要检查构成我身体的每个部分 确认「我」这个存在
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.60,0:30:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都没有的话也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.38,0:30:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「什么都没有」这件事 我也想要去接受
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.31,0:30:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 败给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.45,0:30:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明优柔寡断却又顽固的像石头
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.96,0:31:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随你去了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.91,0:31:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会陪着你的 阿雷鲁亚
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.65,0:31:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随你喜欢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.48,0:31:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天人的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.22,0:31:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想 那是和世界的扭曲进行的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.47,0:31:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7年前 作为学生的我 总觉得战争什么的是很遥远的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.06,0:31:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是世界上有许多的生命被夺去了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.99,0:32:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最重要的东西也是 全部被破坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.90,0:32:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此 也有由懵懂的我造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.08,0:32:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逝去的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.34,0:32:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤兵搬到这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.18,0:32:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意灯光的角度 别让敌人发现
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.78,0:32:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为你们这帮人
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.02,0:32:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你们杀了我们的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.12,0:32:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 他们什么都没做
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.44,0:32:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.40,0:32:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.66,0:32:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…同伴们…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.77,0:32:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才还一起欢笑着的家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.90,0:32:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是何等…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.55,0:32:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何等的愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.60,0:32:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没想过会变成这样的…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.31,0:33:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想远离战争…这种事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.72,0:33:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事情…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.98,0:33:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夺去他们的生命的就是你！
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.57,0:33:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你愚蠢的行为！
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.65,0:33:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「自己是不同的」
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.14,0:33:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「跟自己无关」
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.67,0:33:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「自己所处的是另外一个世界」
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.77,0:33:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这种无视现实的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.14,0:33:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成了不自觉的恶意 招来了这种结果
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.59,0:33:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…没想会…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.18,0:33:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让托勒密上宇宙去？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.29,0:33:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑吧 这种状态下不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.27,0:33:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这么多人的性命…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.09,0:33:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.75,0:33:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我乘坐00出击
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.08,0:33:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡说什么 你的身体还…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.86,0:34:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能阻止卫星兵器的只有00 Raiser
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.85,0:34:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也应该清楚的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.28,0:34:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM Raiser…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.55,0:34:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任务计划拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.71,0:34:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00 Raiser需要驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.99,0:34:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然想拜托拉塞 不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.91,0:34:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到00 Raiser上去
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.61,0:34:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.59,0:34:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这关系到六万条人命
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.95,0:34:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为了守护的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.70,0:34:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功的机率应该很低吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.54,0:34:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 在开始之前我不想放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.91,0:34:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了守护的战斗…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.11,0:34:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与天人相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.40,0:34:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与刹那相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.40,0:34:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得我自己也必须要改变 必须要认真去面对了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.48,0:34:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是为了改变世界
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.21,0:35:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈·库洛斯洛特
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.19,0:35:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要向露易丝开枪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.57,0:35:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这由你决定
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.95,0:35:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争并不仅仅只能破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.44,0:35:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能去创造东西
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.27,0:35:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是这么相信着
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.41,0:35:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的Gundam的话 是可以做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.21,0:35:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后就看你的了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.03,0:35:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…无法扣下扳机
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.64,0:35:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.69,0:35:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了对露易丝不断叫喊以外什么都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.69,0:35:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.74,0:35:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使这样…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.21,0:35:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.51,0:35:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去见她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.14,0:35:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去见露易丝·哈勒维
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.65,0:35:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.19,0:35:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.74,0:36:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好吗 沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.05,0:36:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.15,0:36:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是我 也想找到未来
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.08,0:36:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.00,0:36:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00 刹那·F·塞艾
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.22,0:36:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出击
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.21,0:36:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00 Raiser 沙慈·库洛斯洛特
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.07,0:36:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.35,0:36:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过天人的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.73,0:36:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦政府得到了革新
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.88,0:36:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很缓慢 世界上的国家逐渐走近
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.03,0:36:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各国内的纠纷也逐渐稳定下来
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.85,0:36:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这真的能顺利进行下去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.03,0:37:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为我们有必要继续注视着正在改变的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.52,0:37:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后去思考
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.63,0:37:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思考我们的期望
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.36,0:37:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了得到真正的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.32,0:37:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 露易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.23,0:37:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.12,0:37:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在呼唤我的声音吗
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.65,0:37:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不对
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.50,0:37:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送给维塔的LEVEL 7数据
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.15,0:37:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS的建模数据吗
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.76,0:37:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.48,0:37:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新型的Twin Drive
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.61,0:37:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机体名 00 QAN[T]
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.50,0:37:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那的…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.57,0:37:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.03,0:38:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.42,0:38:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在拉伯尼的伊安先生发来的加密通信
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.22,0:38:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「QAN[T]的开发按照预定进行中」
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.03,0:38:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.10,0:38:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.69,0:38:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「为了新的系统 希望能发来刹那的脑量子波资料」
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.59,0:38:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等会能来一下医疗室吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.04,0:38:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.40,0:38:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的Gundam完成的话
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.37,0:38:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的就会变成没有纷争的世界了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.31,0:38:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.16,0:38:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我只能告诉你这个
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.78,0:38:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我作为变革者的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.52,0:38:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能让人与人之间互相理解的话
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.68,0:38:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会全力去做
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.87,0:38:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才去拜托伊安这么不合理的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.51,0:38:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要勉强哦
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.57,0:39:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.08,0:39:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了未来的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.39,0:39:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在只能进行破坏的我的心中
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.27,0:39:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次萌生出战斗的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.57,0:39:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我强烈地意识到这点的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.10,0:39:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是洛克昂…尼尔·狄兰迪的话
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.11,0:39:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 是那个男人的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.01,0:39:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与我对立的那个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.86,0:39:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古拉哈姆·艾卡的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.57,0:39:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想见你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.44,0:39:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想见你啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.04,0:39:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.37,0:39:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Beam Saber？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.37,0:39:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍华德和达利耶的仇 就让我讨回来吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.82,0:39:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这GN FLAG！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.98,0:39:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通信被？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.63,0:40:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…！
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.11,0:40:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？那个时候的少年？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.94,0:40:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 我和你是被命运的红线所系的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.29,0:40:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 就是战斗的命运！
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.52,0:40:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于理解了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.44,0:40:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那压倒性的性能 夺去了我的心
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.78,0:40:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这份心情
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.73,0:40:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是爱啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.57,0:40:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.46,0:40:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 超越了爱的话
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.98,0:40:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就变成了仇恨
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.84,0:40:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像过于执着的信仰 诱发了内乱那样
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.68,0:40:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你既然知道的话 为什么还要战斗！
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.32,0:40:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你问军人战斗的意义 那简直就是废话啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.42,0:40:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经扭曲了！
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.12,0:40:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扭曲的是你！
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.03,0:40:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是名为Gundam的这个存在！
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.08,0:41:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要打倒你
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.84,0:41:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界什么的怎么样都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.76,0:41:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我自己的意志！
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.15,0:41:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己不也是
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.45,0:41:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界的一部分吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.02,0:41:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 这就是世界的声音！
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.98,0:41:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错了 你只是执着于自我而已
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.32,0:41:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的扭曲 就由我来斩断！
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.13,0:41:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真能说啊 Gundam！
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.50,0:41:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年过去说过 我是扭曲的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.92,0:41:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 他的存在意义只有战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.12,0:41:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我祈望
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.76,0:41:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要跟你战斗！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.36,0:42:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了那极致的胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.17,0:42:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所追求的只有胜利吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.25,0:42:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还能有什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.14,0:42:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.74,0:42:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和未来相连的 明天！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.33,0:42:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀无赦
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.64,0:42:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空手夺白刃？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.76,0:42:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我的 战斗！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.83,0:43:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗吧 少年
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.33,0:43:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斩了我 将胜利握于手中！
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.68,0:43:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.82,0:43:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不刺过来？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.76,0:43:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.89,0:43:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活下去 抓住明天
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.32,0:43:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.14,0:43:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.18,0:43:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了活下去的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.31,0:43:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了活下去的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.21,0:43:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年过去给我留下了这句话
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.38,0:43:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界充满了矛盾
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.04,0:43:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算会引起纷争 也要去面对
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.01,0:43:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.83,0:43:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.05,0:44:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脱下了Mr.武士道的面具 作为古拉哈姆·艾卡
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.25,0:44:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会抹去伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.58,0:44:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那是我的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.55,0:44:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 我为了活下去而战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.38,0:44:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要改变我自身
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.21,0:44:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就如尼尔·狄兰迪所要求那样
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.29,0:44:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像伊奥利亚·肖汉博格所追求的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.78,0:44:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要作为变革者
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.25,0:44:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 作为天人的Gundam Meister活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.48,0:44:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与新的Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.77,0:44:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与我的Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.19,0:44:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与00 QAN[T]一起
